Column.name: BUSINESS_GROUP_ID
Column.commentInRDBMS: Business Group ID associated with location.

Column.name: SHIP_TO_SITE_FLAG
Column.commentInRDBMS: Indicates whether items can be shipped to this location.

Column.name: RECEIVING_SITE_FLAG
Column.commentInRDBMS: Indicates whether this location can be used as a receiving site.

Column.name: BILL_TO_SITE_FLAG
Column.commentInRDBMS: Indicates whether you can bill items to this location.

Column.name: IN_ORGANIZATION_FLAG
Column.commentInRDBMS: Indicates whether this location is an internal site.

Column.name: OFFICE_SITE_FLAG
Column.commentInRDBMS: Indicates whether this location can be used as an office site.

Column.name: DESIGNATED_RECEIVER_ID
Column.commentInRDBMS: Person foreign key - the contact person for this location.

Column.name: TAX_NAME
Column.commentInRDBMS: Default tax code for this location.

Column.name: INACTIVE_DATE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Date after which this location is no longer valid.

Column.name: STYLE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Address style - foreign key to FND_TERRITORIES.

Column.name: REGION_3
Column.commentInRDBMS: Additional address segment - not used by seeded address structures.

Column.name: GLOBAL_ATTRIBUTE_CATEGORY
Column.commentInRDBMS: Global descriptive flexlield structure defining colunm

Column.name: ENTERED_BY
Column.commentInRDBMS: Applications user who created this location; same as CREATED_BY.

Column.name: TP_HEADER_ID
Column.commentInRDBMS: Unsupported in Oracle Human Resources. Used by Oracle EDI Gateway.

Column.name: ECE_TP_LOCATION_CODE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Unsupported in Oracle Human Resources. Used by Oracle EDI Gateway.

Column.name: OBJECT_VERSION_NUMBER
Column.commentInRDBMS: System-generated version of row. Increments by one with each update.
